description: This schedule is applicable to all metered non-residential customers whose Monthly Maximum Demand equals, exceeds, or is expected to equal or exceed 20 kW and is optionally available to common use and metered non-residential customers whose Monthly Maximum Demand is less than 20 kW.
energycomments: DWR-BC stands for Department of Water Resources Bond Charges. Adj accounts for The Electric Energy Commodity Cost (EECC).
